{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC05_COR_050.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x12,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "*Sigh*..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What's wrong, Cory?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "...You're pretty much the only one who shops at my store. Thank you very much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Wait, really? Nobody else is buying stuff from you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Yes, that's right. Hardly anyone buys anything..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "But it's so convenient."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "...It seems my store is only suited for a narrow range of people."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "The main problem is that normal customers don't need items they already have duplicated."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Oh, right. It's convenient because I'm an alchemist. I'd need lots of materials to make the same item over and over."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Yes, most customers want to buy new things. Items they don't already have..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Oh, but maybe people like craftsmen would want to come here? They use lots of the same materials too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "That's true. Besides you, most of the people who come here are that type of person."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Although there aren't many of them..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Then maybe you can find work from Mr. Horst? There's lots of requests for items."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "That's a problem too. I need to have one of an item before I can use my power to duplicate it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I guess I just need to work harder every day, so word of mouth spreads better."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "It's tough running a store."
        }
    ]
}